2\"| Transfer\n!scope=\"col\"| Reference\n|-\n| 1\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Paul Pogba]]\n| \u00a389m{{efn|plus another \u20ac5 million in additional bonuses.}}\n| 2016\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Juventus F.C.|Juventus]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.football-italia.net/88963/official-pogba-signs-man-utd |title=Official: Pogba signs for Man Utd for \u20ac105m |work=[[Football Italia#Website and magazine|Football Italia]] |date=8 August 2016 |accessdate=8 August 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web |title=United Sign Pogba |url=http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2016/Aug/manchester-united-sign-paul-pogba.aspx |website=Official Manchester United Website |accessdate=8 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37016170 |title=Paul Pogba: Manchester United re-sign France midfielder for world-record \u00a389m |work=BBC Sport |date=8 August 2016 |accessdate=8 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Arindam |last=Rej |title=Paul Pogba completes record transfer to Manchester United from Juventus |publisher=ESPN |date=8 August 2016 |url=http://www.espnfc.com/story/2915734/paul-pogba-completes-record-move-to-manchester-united-from-juventus |accessdate=8 August 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harry Maguire]]\n| \u00a380m\n| 2019\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Harry Maguire: Man Utd sign Leicester defender for world record \u00a380m |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49224905 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=5 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Transferts : Harry Maguire, le d\u00e9fenseur le plus cher de l'histoire, \u00e0 Manchester United pour six ans |url=https://www.lequipe.fr/Football/Actualites/Transferts-harry-maguire-